title: Looking for Ranked 5's, Diamond player.
body: Hi, currently looking for a ranked 5's team, where i can play ADC/JG/Support to a high level. At the start of S6 i peaked D2 and soon had to find a job where i didnt play for awhile and dropped to around plat 3. Preferably looking for high elo players, add in game. :) pls camp big d.
